    "description": "Digital Wallet Backend through API Gateway\n\nBase URL: http://localhost:9090\n\nFeatures: JWT Auth, Tiered Rate Limiting (Redis), Request Validation\n\nHeaders enforced by gateway:\n- Content-Type: application/json\n- Channel: WEBP | SWIFTY | BANKAPP | MOBILEMONEY | SAMONEY\n- AppId: <string>\n- AppVersion: <semver>\n- RequestId: <uuid>\n- Authorization: Bearer <jwt> (protected endpoints only)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "12647236",
